data.description: Honey STOP the car! Introducing an exquisite residence that beckons with sophistication and style. Nestled on a private city lot, this captivating home invites you to experience the epitome of comfortable living. Step inside to discover a meticulously designed floor plan that seamlessly blends functionality with elegance. The two bedrooms on one side of the house provide a sense of privacy, while the master suite on the opposite end creates a luxurious retreat. Vaulted ceilings elevate the living space, offering an airy and expansive ambiance. The heart of this home is the stunning open floor plan that encompasses a beautifully appointed kitchen. Revel in the culinary delights facilitated by the granite countertops, complemented by an island that enhances both form and function. The convenience of the laundry room, strategically located near the kitchen and master suite, adds a practical touch to everyday living. Beyond the interior, step into the great flat backyard—a haven for outdoor enthusiasts. A patio awaits for al fresco dining, and a shed, complete with a sink and shelves, provides storage solutions that seamlessly integrate practicality and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home—where every detail reflects a commitment to quality living. All information deemed reliable, but not guaranteed. Square footage, acreage, and taxes are approximate and buyer and buyer's agent to verify.
